WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.190 --> 00:00:03.550
I am going to scream as loud as I can and
I am going to keep screaming as loud as I

00:00:03.550 --> 00:00:07.110
can while I spin around. I will keep going
until my breath runs out.

00:00:07.360 --> 00:00:08.160
&gt;&gt; Great.

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:09.300
&gt;&gt; You ready? &gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:11.480
&gt;&gt; Ok [Screams]

